agarjuna|Nāgārjuna]]||那伽閼剌樹那 (龍樹) / Nàqiéèlàshùnà (Lóngshù)||Na-Già-Át-Lạt-Thụ-Na (Long-Thọ)||Nagaarajuna (Ryūju)||나가알랄수나 (용수) / Nakaallalsuna (Yongsu) |- style="background-color:#F4F9FF;" |15||[[Aryadeva|Āryadeva]] / Kānadeva||迦那提婆 / Jiānàtípó||Ca-Na-Đề-Bà||Kanadaiba||가나제바 / Kanajeba |- style="background-color:#F4F9FF;" |16||Rāhulata||羅睺羅多 / Luóhóuluóduō||La-Hầu-La-Đa||Ragorata||라후라다 / Rahurada |- style="background-color:#F4F9FF;" |17||Sanghānandi||僧伽難提 / Sēngqiénántí||Tăng-Già-Nan-Đề||Sōgyanandai||승가난제 / Sŭngsananje |- style="background-color:#F4F9FF;" |18||Sanghayaśas||僧伽舍多 / Sēngqiéshèduō||Tăng-Già-Da-Xá||Sōgyayasha||가야사다 / Kayasada |- style="background-color:#F4F9FF;" |19||Kumārata||鳩摩羅多 / Jiūmóluóduō||Cưu-Ma-La-Đa||Kumorata (Kumarata)||구마라다 / Kumarada |- style="background-color:#F4F9FF;" |20||Śayata / Jayata||闍夜多 / Shéyèduō||Xà-Dạ-Đa||Shayata||사야다 / Sayada |- style="background-color:#F4F9FF;" |21||[[Vasubandhu]]||婆修盤頭 (世親) / Póxiūpántóu (Shìqīn)||Bà-Tu-Bàn-Đầu (Thế-Thân)||Bashubanzu (Sejin)||바수반두 (세친) / Pasubandu (Sechin) |- style="background-color:#F4F9FF;" |22||Manorhitajuna||摩拏羅 / Mónáluó||Ma-Noa-La||Manura||마나라 / Manara |- style="background-color:#F4F9FF;" |23||Haklenayaśas||鶴勒那 (鶴勒那夜奢) / Hèlènà (Hèlènàyèzhě)||Hạc-Lặc-Na||Kakurokuna (Kakurokunayasha) ||학륵나 / Haklŭkna |- style="background-color:#F4F9FF;" |24||Simhabodhi||師子菩提 / Shīzǐpútí||Sư-Tử-Bồ-Đề / Sư-Tử-Trí||Shishibodai||사자 / Saja |- style="background-color:#F4F9FF;" |25||Vasiasita||婆舍斯多 / Póshèsīduō||Bà-Xá-Tư-Đa||Bashashita||바사사다 / Pasasada |- style="background-color:#F4F9FF;" |26||[[Punyamitra]]||不如密多 / Bùrúmìduō||Bất-Như-Mật-Đa||Funyomitta||불여밀다 / Punyŏmilta |- style="background-color:#F4F9FF;" |27||[[Prajnatara|Prajñātāra]]||般若多羅 / Bōrěduōluó||Bát-Nhã-Đa-La||Hannyatara||반야다라 / Panyadara |- style="background-color:#F4F9FF;" |28||Dharmayana / [[Bodhidharma]]||Ta Mo / [http://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%8F%A9%E6%8F%90%E8%BE%BE%E6%91%A9 菩提達磨 / Pútídámó]||Đạt-Ma / [http://vi.wikipedia.org/wiki/B%E1%BB%93-